metatags.title: prisma
metatags.description: Prisma is an open-source database toolkit. It includes a JavaScript/TypeScript ORM for Node.js, migrations and a modern GUI to view and edit the data in your database. You can use Prisma in new projects or add it to an existing one.. Latest version: 7.2.0, last published: a month ago. Start using prisma in your project by running `npm i prisma`. There are 846 other projects in the npm registry using prisma.
